      <title>三重杠杆的 Nvidia 交易员遭遇 52% 的单日亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/triple-levered-nvidia-traders-are-gutpunched-by-52-one-day-loss</link>
